{
  "stem": "935.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I did not know Avenue Louise, nor did I know where it was if I would have known it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I was there until a Flemish soldier, who [INAUDIBLE] spoke French instead of German, which I already couldn't hear anymore, tapped me on my shoulder and led me to-- down in the dungeon somewhere, into a round cell.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the cell-- and he locked the door, and the cell was full-- full, full, full, full, full.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean really, wall to wall, people standing up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody had luggage instead, only us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all from Belgium.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they told us where we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The thing is that, just before they opened the car and brought us out, I tore up my ID in tiny little papers and threw  it through the blinds, out the window.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't want anybody to know where I am, who I am, what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They can tell me what they want.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I have no IDs, I can tell them what I want too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which I did, by the way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They can't prove anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not that I am, not that I am not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As it turned out, it didn't make much sense, because they found it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You wouldn't believe it, what they are looking for.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's-- it's inconceivable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Really, that's all they have to do for.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was called out of the cell, and there was-- and at that time, it worked out that I didn't understand the importance of uniforms, you know, who was higher ranking, whatever.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I only knew-- you know what [INAUDIBLE] are, the [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had it in German in the student days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a sign of honor, when you were fighting with a saber, to have these signs of whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
